      "duration": 2.42,
      "size": 38736,
      "text": "插入排序像整理扑克牌，把每张牌插进前面已排好的部分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "quick",
      "line_id": "quick-1",
