      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/yunxi/quick-quick-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "快排选一个基准，把比它小的放左边，比它大的放右边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "quick",
      "line_id": "quick-2",
      "filename": "quick-quick-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/yunxi/quick-quick-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "再对左右两半递归地做同样的事，这就是分而治之。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "quick",
      "line_id": "quick-3",
      "filename": "quick-quick-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/yunxi/quick-quick-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.71,
      "size": 27360,
      "text": "平均下来只需 O(n 乘以 log n)，比冒泡快得多。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "merge",
      "line_id": "merge-1",
