      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/yunxi/merge-merge-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "归并排序先把数组一分为二，直到每段只剩一个元素。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "merge",
      "line_id": "merge-2",
      "filename": "merge-merge-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/yunxi/merge-merge-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "再两两合并有序的小段，相等元素保持原序，因此它很稳定。"
    },
